<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "SoftwareApplication",
  "name": "Pagecord",
  "url": "https://pagecord.com",
  "description": "A blogging platform for curious, independent writers. Create a site with home page and powerful blog in seconds. Publish with the rich text editor, email, Obsidian, API, or CLI.",
  "applicationCategory": "BloggingApplication",
  "operatingSystem": "Any (web-based)",
  "offers": [
    {
      "@type": "Offer",
      "name": "Classic",
      "price": "0",
      "priceCurrency": "USD"
    },
    {
      "@type": "Offer",
      "name": "Premium (Annual)",
      "price": "<%= Subscription.price(:annual) %>",
      "priceCurrency": "USD",
      "priceSpecification": {
        "@type": "UnitPriceSpecification",
        "billingDuration": "P1Y"
      }
    },
    {
      "@type": "Offer",
      "name": "Premium (Monthly)",
      "price": "<%= Subscription.price(:monthly) %>",
      "priceCurrency": "USD",
      "priceSpecification": {
        "@type": "UnitPriceSpecification",
        "billingDuration": "P1M"
      }
    }
  ]
}
</script>

<div class="md:mt-4 mb-4 md:mb-8 mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4">
  <h1 class="source-serif font-semibold text-center text-4xl md:text-6xl tracking-tight">
  Blog Without The Slog
  </h1>

  <div class="md:text-xl text-base leading-relaxed text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200 flex flex-col gap-y-4">
    <p class="mt-8 md:mt-12 text-2xl font-bold"><span class="inline bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,transparent_65%,rgb(79_189_156_/_0.3)_65%)] dark:bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,transparent_65%,rgb(79_189_156_/_0.4)_65%)] [box-decoration-break:clone] px-1 -mx-1 leading-relaxed">A personal website and blog... that you'll actually keep updated.</span></p>

    <p>Out with the old, in with the new. A fresh website and blog for you. </p>

    <p>Write where you like, when you like. A powerful text editor, post by email, publish directly from Obsidian. Pagecord meets you where you already write, and stays out of your way.</p>

    <p>Bootstrapped, profitable and proud. No tracking, no lock-in, no AI. Your words, written your way, on your own corner of the web.</p>

    <div class="text-center mt-2 mb-4 md:text-xl">
      <%= link_to new_signup_path do %>
        <div class="mt-2 inline-flex font-medium p-4 rounded-xl shadow-sm btn-primary text-xl">Start writing for free</div>
      <% end %>
      <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400">Trusted by 900+ independent bloggers</p>
    </div>

    <p>
    Check out real sites: <a href="https://yeechie.nl" class="home-link">Yee Chie's Corner</a>,  <a href="https://sylvia.studio/" class="home-link">Syvia's Studio</a>, <a href="https://blog.jsweeting.me/" class="home-link">James' blog</a>, or see what's trending in the <%= link_to "Pagecord Spotlight", spotlight_path, class: "home-link" %>.
    </p>
   </div>
</div>

<%= render "public/screenshots" %>

<!-- Inline Editor Section -->
<div id="post-by-editor" class="mt-16 mb-4 md:mb-8 mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">
  <h2 class="source-serif text-center font-semibold my-8 text-3xl md:text-4xl tracking-tight">Write using a wonderful text editor</h2>

  <p class="md:text-xl leading-relaxed my-5">
  Pagecord comes with a wonderful online text editor. It handles all your text formatting needs, as well as images, galleries, tables, colours, even code blocks with syntax highlighting!
  </p>

  <%= image_tag "home/rich-text-editor.webp",
    alt: "A screenshot of Pagecord's rich text editor",
    width: "1600",
    height: "967" %>
</div>

<!-- Post by Email Section -->
<div id="post-by-email" class="mt-16 mb-4 md:mb-8 mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">
  <h2 class="source-serif text-center font-semibold my-8 text-3xl md:text-4xl tracking-tight">Write posts to your blog from your inbox</h2>

  <p class="md:text-xl leading-relaxed my-5">
  Posting by email is great fun, and it's the most effortless way to blog. Email is right there on all your devices, with a familiar editor and all the <b>formatting</b> <tt>you</tt> <i>need</i>.
  </p>

  <p class="md:text-xl leading-relaxed my-5">
  Click compose, tap out a message, hit send. <a href="https://help.pagecord.com/posting-by-email" class="font-medium underline">Pagecord does the rest</a>.
  </p>
  <%= image_tag "home/gmail-compose.webp",
        alt: "Screenshot of composing a post in Gmail",
        width: "1600",
        height: "967" %>
</div>

<!-- Obsidian, API and CLI Section -->
<div id="obsidian-api" class="mt-16 mb-4 md:mb-8 mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">
  <h2 class="source-serif text-center font-semibold my-8 text-3xl md:text-4xl tracking-tight">Publish from Obsidian, API, or CLI</h2>

  <p class="md:text-xl leading-relaxed my-5">
  If you draft in <a href="https://obsidian.md" class="font-medium underline">Obsidian</a>, the <a href="https://help.pagecord.com/obsidian" class="font-medium underline">official Pagecord plugin</a> publishes your notes straight to your blog. Prefer a terminal, Shortcuts, or your own scripts? Use the <a href="https://help.pagecord.com/api" class="font-medium underline">API</a> or <a href="https://help.pagecord.com/pagecord-cli" class="font-medium underline">Pagecord CLI</a> to publish from the tools you already use.
  </p>

  <%= image_tag "home/obsidian.webp",
        alt: "Screenshot of the composing a post in Obsidian",
        width: "1600",
        height: "1609" %>
</div>

<!-- Newsletter Section -->
<div id="newsletter" class="mt-16 mb-4 md:mb-8 mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">
  <h2 class="source-serif text-center font-semibold my-8 text-3xl md:text-4xl tracking-tight">Your posts, delivered by email</h2>

  <p class="md:text-xl leading-relaxed my-5">
  Premium customers can allow readers to subscribe to their blog by email. Choose between a <strong>weekly digest</strong> that's fully automated, or <strong>individual delivery</strong> where you pick exactly which posts to send.
  </p>
  <p class="md:text-xl leading-relaxed my-5">
  You focus on writing. Pagecord handles the rest. Who needs Substack?
  </p>

  <%= image_tag "home/weekly-digest.webp",
    alt: "A screenshot of Apple Mail with a weekly digest email",
    width: "1600",
    height: "967" %>
</div>

<!-- Analytics Section -->
<div id="analytics" class="mt-16 mb-4 md:mb-8 mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 text-slate-800 dark:text-slate-200">
  <h2 class="source-serif text-center font-semibold my-8 text-3xl md:text-4xl tracking-tight">Privacy-respecting analytics built in</h2>

  <p class="md:text-xl leading-relaxed my-5">
  It's fun to know how many people are visiting your blog, but third-party analytics are fiddly, expensive, and often don't respect privacy.
  </p>
  <p class="md:text-xl leading-relaxed my-5">
  Pagecord Premium has simple, privacy-first analytics built in. And if you'd rather not know, you can turn it all off.
  </p>

  <%= image_tag "home/analytics.webp",
    alt: "A screenshot of Pagecord's page view analytics page",
    width: "1600",
    height: "964" %>
</div>

<!-- Testimonials Section -->
<%= render "testimonials" %>

